<p>There is only one way of having two instruments equipped at the same time and that is to have: <br /> <br /><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=15738" title="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=15738" target="akztarg">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=15738</a> <br /> <br />And then any other instrument, but the chances of getting this drum is low since VT is a quested zone to get access (have to do a long winded key quest) and also the mob doesn't drop it very often. <br /> <br />Hope this helps, otherwise Slipskin is correct.</p>
